<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Sullied Industries | Services</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <nav class="top-nav">
        <a href="index.html">HOME</a>
        <a href="artists.html">ROSTER</a>
        <a href="services.html">SERVICES</a>
        <a href="#" class="nav-login">LOG IN</a>
    </nav>
    <h1>LOGISTICS ARCHITECTURE</h1>
    <p>Professional administration for the independent artist. No middle-man headaches.</p>

    <div class="pricing-grid">
        <div class="tier-card">
            <h3>The Single</h3>
            <span class="tier-price">$XX</span>
            <p>One track. Metadata setup, ISRC routing, and store delivery management.</p>
            <div class="bunker-note">Status: OPEN</div>
        </div>

        <div class="tier-card">
            <h3>The Project</h3>
            <span class="tier-price">$XX</span>
            <p>Full EP or Album. Sequence management, credits audit, and gapless playback check.</p>
            <div class="bunker-note">Status: OPEN</div>
        </div>

        <div class="tier-card" style="border-color: var(--signal-green);">
            <h3>System Retainer</h3>
            <span class="tier-price">$XX/mo</span>
            <p>Unlimited releases. Priority label support. Your personal manager for all active logistics.</p>
            <div class="bunker-note">Status: ACTIVE</div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bunker-note" style="max-width: 600px; margin: 20px auto; text-align: left;">
        <strong>DISTRIBUTION POLICY:</strong> Sullied Industries takes 0% of your royalties. 
        All projects are routed via RouteNote. Choose between 100% Royalty Retention (requires upfront store fee) 
        or 85% Royalty Retention (zero upfront store fee).
    </div>

    <br>
    <a href="mailto:your-sulliedindustries@gmail.com?subject=Service%20Inquiry" class="login-btn">REQUEST ASSISTANCE</a>
    <br><br>
    <a href="index.html">← RETURN TO MAIN SYSTEM</a>
</body>
</html>
